Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是六人吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里是五色光啊！
